{"word":"ἀναιδής","slug":"ἀναιδής","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n6586\" key=\"a)naidh/s\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἀναιδής</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ές</itype>, (<etym lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"etym\">αἰδώς</etym>) <sense id=\"n6586.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shameless,</tr_> of Agamemnon, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὦ μέγ᾽ ἀναιδές</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:158\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.158</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; of Penelope's suitors, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:1:254\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.254</biblScope></bibl>, al.; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὦ θρέμμ᾽ ἀναιδές</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg005.perseus-grc1:622\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ El.\">El.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">622</biblScope></bibl></cit>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n6586.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. gen., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Κυδοιμὸν ἀναιδέα δηϊοτῆτος</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">ruthless</tr_> in havoc, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:5:593\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">5.593</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"II\" id=\"n6586.2\" level=\"2\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of things, as, in <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:11:598\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.598</biblScope></bibl>, the stone of Sisyphus is called <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">λᾶας ἀναιδής</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the reckless, ruthless</tr_> stone, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:521\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.521</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:13:139\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">13.139</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πότμος ἀ.</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg001.perseus-grc1:10(11).105\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pi.\">Pi.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">O.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">10(11).105</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐλπὶς ἀ.</quote_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">greedy,</tr_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0033.tlg003.perseus-grc1:11:45\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">N.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">11.45</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἃ πέπονθ᾽ ἀναιδῆ</foreign> the <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">shame</tr_> that I have suffered, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0011.tlg007.perseus-grc1:516\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ S.\">S.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ O